[The etiology of a cluster of illness at a conference manifesting as a dry throat, sometimes with fever, is not clear and may not be infectious in origin. With an attack rate of 40-50 percent, it may well be possible to assess by questionnaire what risk factors are relevant. ProMED-mail awaits for more information about this illness. - Mod.LL

